{
  "texts": [
    "Wazuh, SIEMonster and Elastic Security use Kibana for dashboards and visualization which is extremely powerful.",
    "The users can create custom graphs and charts according to their requirements.",
    "OSSIM also provides data visualization but it is not as rich as the commercial USM version.",
    "Wazuh provides predefined compliance report templates for standards such as the Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS), General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) and Good Practice Guide 13 (GPG 13).",
    "Elastic Security satisfies Federal Information Processing Standards (FIPS), Federal Information Security Management Act (FISMA), PCI DSS, HIPAA, GDPR, ISO standards."
  ]
}